description: Health officials may recommend further restrictions on Dublin to curb the spread of Covid-19.
title: Coronavirus: Irish county lockdowns 'expected in coming months'
title_page: Coronavirus: Irish county lockdowns 'expected in coming months' - BBC News
maintext: "If we choose to act in relation to Dublin in the next couple of days, far from being slow to act as some would argue, we will be the first movers in Europe in taking action early", Mr Varadkar said.
